			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Also called solar panels, a solar module is a single photovoltaic panel that is an assembly of connected solar cells. The solar cells absorb sunlight as a source of energy to generate electricity. An array of modules are used to supply power to buildings. Residential solar systems use PV panels, which are made up of solar cells that absorb sunlight. The absorbed sunlight creates electrical charges that flow within the cell.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">太阳能电池组件也称为太阳能电池板，是由太阳能电池连接而成的单个光电板。太阳能电池吸收太阳光作为发电能源。模块阵列用于为建筑物供电。住宅太阳能系统使用光伏板，光伏板由吸收阳光的太阳能电池组成。吸收的阳光产生电荷，在电池内流动。</common:generalComment>
